all the hardships are over.

286
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,120
From now on, every day

287
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,550
will be a fresh start.

288
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,740
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

289
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:07,980
[Qiaoxiang Pavilion]

290
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,550
Take care.

291
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,360
Travel safe.

