00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,000
Take care.

295
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,060
Take care.

296
00:12:27,060 --> 00:12:32,100
♪The breezy wind blows,
the heart grows tender and bitter♪

297
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:32,720
Let's go.

298
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:39,620
♪I ask the Sun
if the light has taken root♪

299
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:47,180
♪As it prospers,
our love story writes itself♪

